(62, 1, '2024-04-01 07:24:55', '2024-04-01 07:24:55', '<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">Shoppre’s customers love shopping for Indian wear. And why wouldn’t they? Ethnic wear has a timeless appeal that connects us to our traditions. The regal Indian attires like Anarkali suits, Lehengas, Saree, Bandhgala, Jodhpuri Suits, and Achkan convey a sense of grandeur. Wearing ethnic clothes on Indian occasions is a timeless tradition. They are the highlight of any Indian festival or event.</p>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">All special occasions begin with meticulous planning of the ensembles for the day, a testament to the importance we place on our attire. At Shoppre, the dedication extends to ensuring the secure and timely delivery of your carefully chosen garment to your doorstep. We care about your packages as our own. With access to 1000+ authentic Indian shopping sites, our global clientele benefits from the convenience of shopping directly from India. Your country from India through our shop and ship service, allowing you to enjoy a hassle-free and cost-effective shipping service.</p>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">Let’s look at the wardrobe must-haves with our curated list of our customers’ top ten ethnic wear essentials for men and women, reflecting a perfect blend of tradition and contemporary style.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 id=\"sell-discount\" class=\"font-weight-800 f-s-20 p-color-cement-dark f-siz-14\"></h4>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\n<h4>Anarkali Suit</h4>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">Anarkali Suits and their majestic flair create the perfect symphony of silhouette and style befitting any Indian occasion. The <a href=\"https://www.myntra.com/kurtas/rangeelo/rangeelo-geometric-printed-chanderi-silk-anarkali-kurta-with-dupatta/24904764/buy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chanderi silk Anarkali suit set by Rangeelo</a> is everything you need. It blends modern geometric print trends with ethnic color elements, a captivating fusion of style and comfort