(77, 1, '2024-04-02 08:17:05', '2024-04-02 08:17:05', '<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">Sankranti is an auspicious festival from the Indian states of Telangana and Andhra Pradesh that marks a fresh beginning, the commencement of a new era or year. Like other Indian festivals, people embrace Sankranti with pomp, joyous celebrations, delicious food, and accompanied by happiness. Getting dressed in traditional attires, decorating homes with Rangoli, and visiting temples are among the many rituals people follow to usher in this new beginning.</p>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">Embark on a fashion journey with the dawn of a new year. Elevate your wardrobe with a touch of tradition and grace with fresh fashion essentials for the new year. Celebrate Sankranti with Shoppre’s top picks for the festive season that blends culture and trend seamlessly.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Women\'s Wardrobe Essentials for Sankranti</h4>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/SAREE-MALL-WomenS-Blouse-Pink_Free/dp/B079PYDYDC/ref=sr_1_21?fst=as%3Aoff&amp;pf_rd_i=14670558031&amp;pf_rd_m=AT95IG9ONZD7S&amp;pf_rd_p=6ce1e2e1-9f00-46a1-a59f-0e031079d0cd&amp;pf_rd_r=5H3MJRADMPNXBEK2BGCQ&amp;pf_rd_s=merchandised-search-7&amp;pf_rd_t=101&amp;qid=1704816582&amp;refinements=p_n_pct-off-with-tax%3A40-%2Cp_98%3A10440597031&amp;rnid=10440596031&amp;rps=1&amp;s=apparel&amp;sr=1-211\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Pink silk Saree</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\">A silk Saree is a must-have piece for your wardrobe because of its timeless allure and sophistication that transcends time. It is an exquisite choice for any traditional occasion or event, effortlessly making you the center of attention. The inherent richness and intricate craftsmanship embody ethnic charm, making it the perfect ethnic essential for starting the new year.</p>\r\n<p class=\"header4 p-color-cement\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.in/Yellow-Chimes-Jewellery-Traditional-Necklace/d